message: Focus on cooking raw ingredients with the stove first; this typically gives 20 value per item. Then, combine two cooked items that are culinarily compatible (like cooked protein and cooked vegetable) for a significant value boost, often to 60. You can sometimes add a third compatible cooked item for an even higher score (e.g., 80).
